    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground cumin</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
