    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained red kidney beans</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped sweet potato </strong>and<strong> soy stock</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the sweet potato is cooked through – this is your <strong>plant-based chilli</strong></p>",
