    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> tortilla triangles</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then spread them out and put the tray[s] in the oven for 6-8 min or until lightly browned and crisp – these are your <strong>nachos</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
